  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Lost Life : Origins\"</strong> is a first-person survival horror experience that blends psychological tension, environmental storytelling, and strategic combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You awaken in a burning forest. Bleeding, broken, alone. Smoke coils through the trees, making it harder to breathe, while the flames feel otherworldly cold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/483b812f1547fd1685e35bc3899bd633.poster.avif?t=1761943672\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/483b812f1547fd1685e35bc3899bd633.webm?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/483b812f1547fd1685e35bc3899bd633.mp4?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drawn toward a fog-shrouded town, you begin to sense the fracture: reality warps, memories blur, and the world is shifting around you, unleashing horrors that twist the familiar into the grotesque and broken.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something is unraveling, and you’re trapped within its collapse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/979537228959a16b7b124e497369295e.poster.avif?t=1761943672\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/979537228959a16b7b124e497369295e.webm?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/979537228959a16b7b124e497369295e.mp4?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◽ <strong>Uncover a Story Hidden in the Mist</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story is told through what you do, what you notice, symbolism, and the environment itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every object and sound might be a clue to a bigger picture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Piece together fragmented memories, and read between the lines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/8558af1429fb1ca191d9e923614dfa53.poster.avif?t=1761943672\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/8558af1429fb1ca191d9e923614dfa53.webm?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/8558af1429fb1ca191d9e923614dfa53.mp4?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>◽ <strong>Explore</strong> <strong>Semi-Open World</strong>,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a fractured town where every alley, corner, and corridor hides secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden events and locations that may change based on your actions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/2b0d3c6af001d478be98acd74d777d24.poster.avif?t=1761943672\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/2b0d3c6af001d478be98acd74d777d24.webm?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/2b0d3c6af001d478be98acd74d777d24.mp4?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◽<strong>Observe</strong>, <strong>Investigate</strong>, <strong>Survive</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world speaks. You just have to listen to it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look around and search for clues that lead you through the town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your strength lies not is combat, but in observation and awareness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/06489ed071e2e77adb82248a62128b60.poster.avif?t=1761943672\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/06489ed071e2e77adb82248a62128b60.webm?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/06489ed071e2e77adb82248a62128b60.mp4?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◽ <strong>Customize Through Discovery</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find rare collectibles that enhance your stats, unlock hidden paths, or alter future encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices shape your experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/1c9011361a2226dee7f581addc67a9c0.poster.avif?t=1761943672\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/1c9011361a2226dee7f581addc67a9c0.webm?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/1c9011361a2226dee7f581addc67a9c0.mp4?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◽ <strong>Strategic Combat Against Diverse Enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The monsters here are not just enemies, but echoes of something deeper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each one moves differently, thinks differently, dies differently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every encounter adds a note to your Bestiary, a growing record of their strengths, weaknesses, and behaviors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Study it well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/729d6839750feca6dd054575ff809e2c.poster.avif?t=1761943672\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/729d6839750feca6dd054575ff809e2c.webm?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/729d6839750feca6dd054575ff809e2c.mp4?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◽ <strong>Stealth is an Option.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some foes demand pure aggression, others may require stealth and patience. Know when to fight and when to flee.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each enemy reacts differently, so adapt your tactics to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use darkness, silence, and misdirection to evade threats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/80370dbe8fc0b4222dea9fb53a939d88.poster.avif?t=1761943672\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/80370dbe8fc0b4222dea9fb53a939d88.webm?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/80370dbe8fc0b4222dea9fb53a939d88.mp4?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◽<strong>Traverse Shifting Realities.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you descend deeper, reality fractures, revealing alternate dimensions, distorted memories, and impossible architecture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The truth demands sacrifice. Adapt or be consumed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/3555b615a7e7e696dd7886e8e5213a1a.poster.avif?t=1761943672\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/3555b615a7e7e696dd7886e8e5213a1a.webm?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/3555b615a7e7e696dd7886e8e5213a1a.mp4?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◽ <strong>Railgun customization</strong> options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/8eced5a5f4990bc9ab236366d224fb4a.poster.avif?t=1761943672\" width=852 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/8eced5a5f4990bc9ab236366d224fb4a.webm?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2020180/extras/8eced5a5f4990bc9ab236366d224fb4a.mp4?t=1761943672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Lost Life : Origins\" invites you to step into the unknown, where every choice echoes across realities. As the world shatters, it's twisted memories manifest, warping familiar streets into nightmares.</strong></p>",
